{"tid":1691530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【區選攻略】(即日至投票日)","createTime":"2019-11-03T16:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T23:50:25.000Z","uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1d31c088918e40cc92ac5c71d95d9f3be62fcadf","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"區議會雖然係諮詢架構，但亦都係由政府手中得到資源既最直接方法之一，你既一票，就決定未來四年資源誰屬，所以，<span style=\"color: red;\">記得投票</span>。<br />\n<br />\n以下會分三節，講下由即日至選舉日既時間表，畀大家參考下<br />\n<br />\n第一節  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【即做篇】</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一. 幫自己同屋企人睇清楚選區<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fweb%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=ce7cf4c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/web/</a> <br />\n好多人可能搬屋等等既原因，未必係自己屋企既所屬選區，所以第一件事，睇清楚選區<br />\n二. 睇清楚票站同候選人資料，揀定心水，如果有假獨立或者撞區而唔識揀，請睇以下網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://vote4.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvote4.hk%2F&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=23f5c47c\" target=\"_blank\">https://vote4.hk/</a><br />\n <br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n第二節 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【選前篇】</span></span><br />\n一. 確定交通路線<br />\n研究由屋企到票站既來回路線。選舉當日，可能TG放題、黑警橫行，當日盡早投票，最好用公共交通出入，以免全世界揸車和你塞<br />\n二. 了解親戚朋友立場<br />\n自己友就提佢投票，如果立場唔同，嘗試說服。說服唔到，就幫佢制訂行程，例如去海洋公園、一日遊、美食之旅，令佢唔得閒投票。<br />\n三. 在地<del>革命</del> 拉票<br />\n聯絡樓下既候選人，睇下有冇野要幫手，多多益善、少少無拘，例如平日07:45坐車返工，可以早幾個字落樓，幫佢做下街站，夠鐘再上車。總之抗爭同生存為先，行有餘力不妨幫手拉票。<br />\n<br />\n==================<br />\n<br />\n第三節<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【選舉日】</span></span><br />\n一. 盡早投票，最好下晝兩點之前投完票，再食個飽飯<br />\n二. 提醒親戚朋友投票<br />\n三. 為免返唔到屋企，盡快返去自己住既區，幫樓下候選人拉票<br />\n四. 如果第二日放假，或者睏唔著，可以幫手監票"},{"pid":"0e5dff0be7c4ad8a968d383f1ce0f5f996a9f450","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:45:24.000Z","msg":"P牌自推兩野"},{"pid":"ccd5d3d80cdc3d6d735fca14a28abfe9ea26ec94","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"曱甴近平  曱甴王甴近平"},{"pid":"c9360bfadc189aa84102a438a05baa9566d7c840","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"習近平曱甴"},{"pid":"f9ec73e12fc4d98347f82a6c675d30470f56f008","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"推返上黎"},{"pid":"9f6ca5c08b66e215527dc5aaeb41c9784ce906c6","tid":1691530,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"齊齊諗下點拉票呀！拉票對像包括大陸移民，要令佢哋認同<span style=\"color: red;\">自由民主</span>既寶貴。"},{"pid":"7d80fa41499562c7f8d1d7c0605c72448baea5d3","tid":1691530,"uid":36807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T03:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a19d2c653a6b4ebc4c6239b13323772afe9d88cb","tid":1691530,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"係咁易推"}]}